---
title: Citrus Mojo Pork Burgers with Pickles, Zesty Mayo & Roasted Potato Wedges
description: Get your dinner mojo back with this flavorful burger! “Mojo” here actually refers to a citrusy, garlicky sauce beloved by many in the Caribbean. It’s typically used as a marinade for roasted pork, but ours gets folded into juicy pork patties AND stirred into mayo for an unforgettable topping. Served with roasted potato wedges on the side, this meal guarantees good dinner vibes only!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/citrus-mojo-pork-burgers-e56f23ce.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/citrus-mojo-pork-burgers-62a7575983b797737c005246-560e1a17.pdf
servings: 2
time required: 35 minutes
author: HelloFresh
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/citrus-mojo-pork-burgers-62a7575983b797737c005246
nutrition:
  calories: 1100 kcal
